## Downsides


The downsides include:
*LIST
* The M1 Chip lags behind other M-series chip if you do heavy AI or Gaming (Who does that?)
* The 13 inch screen can get small if you do split screen multitasking such ass having one window Godot and another the tutorial, most macs have a similar issue either way, unless you have an iMac
* There may be slow downs if you somewhat push it to its limits with multitasking as the swap is still slower than ram

